    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>rice noodles</strong> to a pot and cover with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Set aside for 12-15 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, drain the <strong>noodles </strong>and run them under <strong>cold running water</strong> and set aside for later</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1608567180127-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
