      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> chilli relish</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar </strong>and <strong>soy sauce </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[75ml]</span> <strong>water</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong></p>",
